#ident	"@(#)bkrs:bkintf.d/backups/bksetup/summary/Help	1.2"

ABSTRACT: Summary Report of Backup Table
	The "summary" task displays a summary report of a backup table.  This
	report displays the rotation period, current week, originating
	device, tag, weeks, days, method, method options, priority and
	destination device information from the backup table you specify.

TITLE: Summary Report of Backup Table

F1:
	"Table:"  Enter the name of the backup table whose entries you want
	to display.  You must enter a path to an existing file.

F2:
	"Week(s):"  Enter a list of week ranges  or the keyword "demand" or
	the keyword "all".  This value will be used to filter the display.
	Only entries with weeks values included in this field will be
	displayed.

F3:
	"Day(s):"  Enter a list of day ranges or the keyword "all".  This
	value will be used with the Weeks value to filter the display.  Only
	those entries with days values included in this field will be
	displayed.  Note that if the value "demand" is entered in the Weeks
	field, no value may be entered in this field.
